<!DOCTYPE html>

SYNTAX :
<html></html>
<head></head>
<body></body>

BEACONS : 
<title>						define the window title (in the head)
<style></style> 			style define (in the head)
<br/>		  	 	  		= '\n'
<hr/>		  	 	  		separator

OPTIONS:
<body bgcolor="color"; background="url">
<div class="NAME"></div>	define a class
<div id="NAME"></div>		define an id
<div style="style">			define the div style
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="doft.css">
<img src="src" alt="name"	print an img (hove is possible)
<form action="" method=""><input type="" name="" placeholder="" value="" method=""> search bar
<li> list

<select><option value="name">name</option></select> deroul. list

TAB:
<table>						create a tab
<tr>						create new cell in the tab
<th>						new header in the cell (center + bold) (opt: colspan="" => col width)
<td>						new data in the cell (left-align + normal)
colspan="x"					the cell will take x normal case

#name (for define id)
.name {
margin: 1px; (possible margin-top/right/left/bottom)
padding: 1px;
border: 1px;
}

text-align: center/left/right/justify
color:
font-size:1px
font-style: normal/italic/oblique
font-weight: normal/bold/lighter
font-family:Courrier/Monospace/Arial....

ADAPTIVE FONT:
1vw = 1% of the window width
1vh = 1% of the window height
1vmin = the smaller between vw/vh
1vmin = the larger between vw/vh
OTHERS (padding/margin/width/height) : just put it in %